



###########################################################################################################################


Http Method					 				CRUD Action

1) POST   | /api/customers 				| Create a new customer
2) GET    | /api/customers 				| Read a list of all customers
3) GET    | /api/customers/{customerId} | Read a single customer
4) PUT    | /api/customers				| Update an existing customer
5) DELETE | /api/customers/{customerId} | Delete a single customer








